## Dataset
The dataset used in this project is the **Social Media Engagement Dataset**, which simulates social media engagement across various metrics.

 [Social Media Engagement Dataset (Kaggle)](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/amritpal333/social-media-engagement-dataset)

### Key Features
- Likes, shares, comments, and impressions
- Sentiment scores & toxicity analysis
- Buzz frequency and engagement growth
- Designed for analysis of **user behavior, trend prediction, and public sentiment**

